[normal]The te
[normal]xt in the following 
[normal]section presents 
[normal]the 
[normal]idea of
[normal] Syste
[normal]ms Thinking 
[normal]Approach to 
[normal]Safety. 
[normal]This a
[normal]pproach was presented by author in hi
