[normal]Author has noted that risk of death from a cardio vascular heart 
[normal]disease (
[normal]CVD) 
[normal]is greater than risk than death from a cycle accident
[normal]. It is expected by World Health Organisation that 
[normal]some 23
[normal].3 million deaths are likely
[normal] due to 
