[normal]’s unreliable performance in
[normal] creating a collusion situation = 13/13+25= .3411 or 34%. 
[normal]The rest 66% contribution to danger 
[normal]can be attributed to road users and other authorities. 
[normal]This way of calculation can be
[normal] 
[normal]evaluated using the example of accident analysis given by the Bayesian inference 
[normal]by Nobel laureate Daniel Kahneman
